01:41:45.000 --> 01:41:48.959
l knew there was something wrong.
l had to find out.

01:41:50.840 --> 01:41:55.868
l followed you both for days.
l meant to kill you.

01:41:55.960 --> 01:41:58.554
l wouldn't talk now.
The ambulance is coming.

01:42:03.280 --> 01:42:05.032
Kit.

01:42:10.000 --> 01:42:11.752
Here, darling.

01:42:14.680 --> 01:42:16.511
lnspector?

